1095
01:15:10,130 --> 01:15:11,769
Everyone, please exit. I'm sorry.

1096
01:15:11,770 --> 01:15:12,770
Oh, come one.

1097
01:15:13,700 --> 01:15:14,940
That was a close call.

1098
