I'm sorry.

1101
01:15:23,110 --> 01:15:24,150
I'm sorry.

1102
01:15:44,370 --> 01:15:46,840
If I'm late, I'm on cleaning duty again.

1103
01:15:47,910 --> 01:15:49,970
I'll take the next bus, and...

1104
01:15:51,340 --> 01:15:53,010
Would it be faster if I can transfer?

1105
01:17:36,050 --> 01:17:38,680
