1109
01:18:04,070 --> 01:18:05,239
It doesn't matter to me.

1110
01:18:05,240 --> 01:18:06,409
It does for me.

1111
01:18:06,410 --> 01:18:07,480
Don't come looking for me again.

1112
01:18:07,880 --> 01:18:09,110
Let me ask you one thing.

1113
01:18:09,210 --> 01:18:11,419
Is there a bus conductor named Seo Jong Yeon here?

1114
01:18:11,420 --> 01:18:15,319
A strange man came looking for someone called Seo Jong Yeon.

1115
01:18:15,320 --> 01:18:16,619
What's going on, Jong Hee?

1116
01:18:16,620 --> 01:18:17,960
- We can't stop. - Stop!

1117
01:18:18,260 --> 01:18:19,519
We have to go faster.

1118
01:18:19,520 --> 01:18:21,760
- Stop! - Please, leave me alone.

1119
01:18:21,860 --> 01:18:24,900
I'm already embarrassed as is, that everyone knows.

1120
01:18:25,000 --> 01:18:26,099
Let go!

1121
01:18:26,100 --> 01:18:28,100
Let me stay by your side, even just as a friend.
